Package: sptotal
Type: Package
Title: Predicting Totals and Weighted Sums from Spatial Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Higham", "Matt", email = "highamm@oregonstate.edu", role = "cre"),
    person("Frank", "Bryce", email = "bryce.frank@oregonstate.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Mauro", "Paco", email = "pmaurogut@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Ver Hoef", "Jay", email = "jay.verhoef@noaa.gov", role = "aut"),
    person("Madsen", "Lisa", email = "lisa.madsen@oregonstate.edu", role = "aut"))
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Maintainer: Matt Higham <highamm@oregonstate.edu>
Description: This package performs predictions of totals and weighted sums, or finite population block kriging, on spatial  data. The primary outputs are an estimate of the total, mean, or weighted sum, in the region, an estimated prediction variance, and a map of the predicted and observed values.
